OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FPhotographer stops time to 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fsnap butterflies and birds 
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A wildlife photographer has revealed   
OL,6, how living with a cancer diagnosis led 
OL,7, him to develop techniques to "make time
OL,8, stop" as he captures stunning images of
OL,9, butterflies and birds.                 
OL,11,FAndrew Fusek Peters, from Shropshire,  
OL,12,Fsaid he had taken up photography as a  
OL,13,Fhobby after his work as a children's   
OL,14,Fauthor had become very stressful.      
OL,16,F"I got very, very ill - mentally - and 
OL,17,FI burned," he explained, "coming       
OL,18,Fthrough that very dark period in my    
OL,19,Flife I knew I had to do something      
OL,20,Felse."                                 
